AUTOPARRY: Toggle automatic parrying in combat

Syntax: autoparry [on|off]

DESCRIPTION:
  Toggles automatic parrying. When enabled, your character will attempt to
  parry incoming melee attacks each round. Parrying costs 1 APM per attempt.

  Parry bonus is based on Physical Prowess (PP): +1 per PP above 10.

  autoparry    : toggles on/off
  autoparry on : enables auto-parry
  autoparry off: disables auto-parry

SEE ALSO: autododge, dodge, parry, combat
